About Us

.entry-hero
Office Hours 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM Monday-Friday
(850)
716-2892
Forest Grove RV Park is the sister property of Cozy Corner RV Lodge which is located at 1815 Hurlburt Road, Ft Walton Beach, Fl. 32547. Cozy Corner RV Lodge opened in the summer of 2019 and we have enjoyed seeing old faces and new ones at our that facility.
Forest Grove RV Park is now open as well and is located at 1318 Lewis Turner Boulevard, Fort Walton Beach, FL, previously known as the Beal Street Extension. We look forward to meeting lots of new folks and seeing old friends at both of our beautiful RV resorts.
.entry-content
